column5: I have had this unit laying around for a long time but have never used it. Problem is that I do not have a power cable or a transducer for it. I can make a power cable but I can't find a transducer anywhere online. Does anybody on here have an old one laying around or perhaps know of a comparable transducer that could work? Possibly the magna 2 ?  Thanks
I ain't got no parts for you sorry. But I have had good luck selling my old finders on ebay then using the money to help pay for the new ones. Even the real old ones too.
Look around and you will find, pretty sure this should fit yours. http://www.ebay.com/itm/LEI-LOWRANCE-EAGLE-HS-WS-TRANSDUCER-PART-90-36-NEW-/221328471348
